---
/**
 * Features Section — 6 张功能卡片
 */
---

<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-badge">
        <i data-lucide="layers" class="icon-xs"></i>
        What You Get
      </span>
      <h2>Everything you need after the first answer</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Start with a city search, then go deeper only when you need more context for your walk, shoot, commute, or prayer plan.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card glass-card" id="feature-sunrise">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-sunrise">
          <i data-lucide="sunrise" class="icon-lg"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Today&apos;s Times, Fast</h3>
        <p>Search a city and land straight on today&apos;s sunrise, sunset, daylight length, and local date without digging through menus.</p>
        <a href="#search" class="feature-link" aria-label="Search for a city">
          Explore data
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="icon-xs"></i>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card glass-card" id="feature-golden">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-golden">
          <i data-lucide="camera" class="icon-lg"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Golden Hour Tracking</h3>
        <p>See morning and evening golden hour first, then layer in twilight and daylight trends only if you need the extra detail.</p>
        <a href="#planner" class="feature-link" aria-label="See golden hour features">
          Plan your shoot
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="icon-xs"></i>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card glass-card" id="feature-moon">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-moon">
          <i data-lucide="moon" class="icon-lg"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Moon Phase & Illumination</h3>
        <p>Check how bright the moon is tonight, when it rises, and whether it helps or hurts the kind of outdoor plan you are making.</p>
        <a href="#planner" class="feature-link" aria-label="See moon phase features">
          View moon data
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="icon-xs"></i>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card glass-card" id="feature-prayer">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-prayer">
          <i data-lucide="clock" class="icon-lg"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Prayer Time Support</h3>
        <p>See the full prayer schedule for the city you searched, plus the next upcoming prayer, without leaving the same page.</p>
        <a href="#planner" class="feature-link" aria-label="See prayer time features">
          Check times
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="icon-xs"></i>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card glass-card" id="feature-daylight">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-daylight">
          <i data-lucide="bar-chart-3" class="icon-lg"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Daylight Trend Clarity</h3>
        <p>See whether the days are getting longer or shorter this week, which matters more than a generic dashboard when you are planning around light.</p>
        <a href="#planner" class="feature-link" aria-label="See daylight analytics">
          See trends
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="icon-xs"></i>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card glass-card" id="feature-speed">
        <div class="feature-icon icon-speed">
          <i data-lucide="gauge" class="icon-lg"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>No Signup, Just Search</h3>
        <p>Open the site, type a city, and move on. The fastest experience is the one that gets out of your way after the answer appears.</p>
        <a href="#search" class="feature-link" aria-label="Search a city now">
          Search now
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="icon-xs"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
